Expressiveness means you waste less of people&#x27;s time and mental effort.<p><pre><code>    $(&quot;.enemy&quot;).after(&#x27;<div class=&quot;crash&quot;>&#x27;).remove()
</code></pre>
Without jQuery:<p><pre><code>    var enemies = document.querySelectorAll(&quot;.enemy&quot;)
    for (var i = 0; i < enemies.length; i++) {
        var div = document.createElement(&quot;div&quot;);
        div.className = &quot;crash&quot;;
        enemies[i].parentNode.insertBefore(div, enemies[i]);
        enemies[i].parentNode.removeChild(enemies[i]);        
    }
